title: Pradhan Mantri Jan Dhan Yojana (PMJDY)
summary: Universal bank accounts and financial inclusion.
eligibility: All unbanked citizens.
benefits: Zero-balance accounts, RuPay card, overdraft.

title: Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala Yojana (PMUY)
summary: LPG connections for BPL households.
eligibility: Women from BPL households.
benefits: Free LPG connection with subsidy.

title: National Social Assistance Programme (NSAP)
summary: Pension support for vulnerable groups.
eligibility: Senior citizens, widows, persons with disabilities.
benefits: Monthly pension transfers.

title: Stand Up India Scheme
summary: Loans for SC/ST and women entrepreneurs.
eligibility: SC/ST and women entrepreneurs.
benefits: Bank loans from 10-100 lakh.

title: Deen Dayal Upadhyaya Grameen Kaushalya Yojana (DDU-GKY)
summary: Skilling and placement for rural youth.
eligibility: Rural youth 15-35.
benefits: Skill training and jobs.

title: National Means-cum-Merit Scholarship (NMMS)
summary: Scholarship to meritorious students from EWS.
eligibility: Class 9 to 12 students from EWS.
benefits: Annual scholarship.

title: AICTE Pragati Scholarship for Girls
summary: Scholarship for girls in technical education.
eligibility: Girl students in AICTE approved institutions.
benefits: Tuition support and contingency.

title: PM POSHAN (Mid-Day Meal)
summary: Nutrition support in schools.
eligibility: Children in government schools.
benefits: Free cooked meals.

title: National Apprenticeship Promotion Scheme (NAPS)
summary: On the job training with stipend support.
eligibility: Apprentices and establishments.
benefits: Stipend reimbursement.

title: Atal Pension Yojana (APY)
summary: Voluntary pension for unorganised workers.
eligibility: Adults 18-40 years with bank account.
benefits: Assured pension post 60.

title: National Programme for Health Care of Elderly (NPHCE)
summary: Dedicated elderly healthcare services.
eligibility: Senior citizens.
benefits: Geriatric OPDs and services.

title: National Youth Policy Initiatives
summary: Support for youth engagement and skilling.
eligibility: Youth 15-29.
benefits: Skill and leadership programs.

title: Beti Bachao Beti Padhao
summary: Awareness and girl child education.
eligibility: Girl children and communities.
benefits: Awareness, education incentives.

title: Pradhan Mantri Matru Vandana Yojana (PMMVY)
summary: Maternity benefit of INR 5000.
eligibility: Pregnant and lactating women.
benefits: Cash incentive for first child.

title: One Stop Centre (Sakhi)
summary: Support to women affected by violence.
eligibility: Women in distress.
benefits: Integrated support services.

title: Transgender Persons (Protection of Rights) Schemes
summary: Welfare measures for transgender persons.
eligibility: Transgender persons.
benefits: Scholarships, skill and shelter

title: Ayushman Bharat - PM-JAY
summary: Health insurance upto INR 5 lakh.
eligibility: Eligible poor families.
benefits: Cashless treatment.

title: Pradhan Mantri Jan Aushadhi Yojana
summary: Affordable generic medicines.
eligibility: All citizens.
benefits: Discounted generics.

title: Mission Indradhanush
summary: Universal immunization of children.
eligibility: Children and pregnant women.
benefits: Free vaccination drives.

title: Pradhan Mantri Shram Yogi Maandhan (PM-SYM)
summary: Pension for unorganised workers.
eligibility: Workers 18-40 with monthly income <=15000.
benefits: Assured pension post 60.

title: e-SHRAM Portal
summary: National database for unorganised workers.
eligibility: Unorganised workers.
benefits: UAN and welfare access.
